  <h2>Padding</h2>
  <div id="buttonDiv">
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-0">Hello</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-1">Hello</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-2">Hello</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-3">Hello</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-4">Hello</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-5">Hello</button>
  </div>
  <p>Here they all have padding of 0, and padding of 5 on the side or sides of their name.</p>
  </p>
  <div id="buttonDiv">
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-0 pt-5">Top</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-0 pr-5">Right</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-0 pb-5">Bottom</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-0 pl-5">Left</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-0 px-5">X axis</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary p-0 py-5">Y axis</button>
  </div>
  <p>Here it changes depending on the screen size. The first changes all sides to the same amount of padding.</p>
  <p>It has 0 padding, then 1 for small screens, 2 for medium, 3 for large and 4 for extra large.</p>
  <div id="buttonDiv"><button class="btn btn-danger p-0 p-sm-1 p-md-2 p-lg-3 p-xl-4 ">Change sizes with screen
      size.</button></div>
  <h2>Margin</h2>
  <p>The exact same examples, but replacing p with m. (Paragraph for Margin)</p>
  <div id="buttonDiv">
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-0">Hello</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-1">Hello</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-2">Hello</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-3">Hello</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-4">Hello</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-5">Hello</button>
  </div>
  <p>Here they all have padding of 0, and padding of 5 on the side or sides of their name.</p>
  </p>
  <div id="buttonDiv">
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-0 mt-5">Top</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-0 mr-5">Right</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-0 mb-5">Bottom</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-0 ml-5">Left</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-0 mx-5">X axis</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary m-0 my-5">Y axis</button>
  </div>
  <div id="buttonDiv"><button class="btn btn-danger m-0 m-sm-1 m-md-2 m-lg-3 m-xl-4 ">Change sizes with screen
